HEADWORD: Autocratical
<hw>Au`to*crat"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to autocracy
or to an autocrat; absolute; holding independent and arbitrary powers of
government.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Au`to*crat"ic*al*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

